        "note": "이거 = this (near me 🙋)\n그거 = that (near you 👂)\n저거 = that over there (far 👉)\n'이거 맛있어요!' = This is delicious!"
      }
    },
    {
      "speaker": "dongsaeng",
      "text": "잘 먹었습니다, 엄마!",
